{"id":232897415,"title":"培根蛋麵（carbonara)","content":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/76e4d435-dec5-43b9-951f-ddeeaa8c5030/1280.jpeg\n\n\n培根蛋麵（carbonara ）\n\n食材：\n培根 兩片\n一顆蛋\n起司粉 半勺火鍋湯匙\n黑胡椒粉 2湯匙\n義大利綜合香料 適量\n洋蔥 1/4顆\n義大利麵 一人份\n蒜頭 一瓣\n奶油 一小塊\n\n作法：\n1.洋蔥 蒜頭切丁 培根切莫\n2.蛋打散 再放入起司粉攪拌均勻（如果喜歡起司味重一點可以再加一些）\n3.麵先放入滾水滾 水先加鹽 橄欖油（麵照包裝只是做 我的是煮11分鐘）\n煮5分鐘的時候撈1/3杯的煮麵水\n4.倒約一湯匙的橄欖油 開小火下培根 炒3分鐘之後下洋蔥 炒6分鐘後下蒜頭 炒均勻後倒約2-3湯匙的胡椒粉 炒均後下煮麵水 關火 奶油放入\n5.把煮好的麵撈起來放進去鍋子先拌勻 拌勻之後再放入剛剛的起司蛋液攪拌均勻 撒上點義大利綜合香料再拌勻\n\nhttps://instagram.com/practicecooking?igshid=kzsz0c41tzug","excerpt":"培根蛋麵（carbonara ），食材：培根 兩片，一顆蛋，起司粉 半勺火鍋湯匙，黑胡椒粉 2湯匙，義大利綜合香料 適量，洋蔥 1/4顆，義大利麵 一人份，蒜頭 一瓣，奶油 一小塊，作法：1.洋蔥 蒜","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-15T15:59:44.716Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T15:59:44.716Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":39,"tags":[],"topics":["烹飪","美食","在家輕鬆做"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"南臺科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":38},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/76e4d435-dec5-43b9-951f-ddeeaa8c5030/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"2d7f9e4b-c975-402b-bdd4-9dbbde0faae2","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/76e4d435-dec5-43b9-951f-ddeeaa8c5030/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/76e4d435-dec5-43b9-951f-ddeeaa8c5030/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/76e4d435-dec5-43b9-951f-ddeeaa8c5030/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-15T15:59:44.716Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T15:59:4